{"tid":1797752,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解分手總係不明不白？","createTime":"2019-12-25T16:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T07:48:32.000Z","uid":209657,"like":144,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"7b261995b00f51bb1b854317213702c79cb01065","tid":1797752,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"大家都無好好講清楚 就分開<br />\n即使我主動問 對方都唔想回應<br />\n又或者偶爾傾兩句 <br />\n但無人會想講返起件事<br />\n<br />\n明明大家一齊嗰陣 視對方咁重要<br />\n點解要告別曾經咁重要既人<br />\n但完全唔會想講清楚再走<br />\n<br />\n其實我都只係想要一個答案<br />\n點解要留一個懸念俾我<br />\n仲好似係一世都拆解唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d915b6afcb891aba555c4c96ff27ecae8964a902","tid":1797752,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"單身既人都要聖誕快樂<br />\n一個人食聖誕大餐都可以好開心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8678d2c0167eeac08b9c3d25eca4bddf2b11e5","tid":1797752,"uid":53730,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:40:08.000Z","msg":"你唔會想佢講得咁清楚<br />\n再講得多都係大話<br />\n仲難受"},{"pid":"e2467f76c785e75de9ead67833c6ff43ed91c0e2","tid":1797752,"uid":228341,"like":29,"dislike":6,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:42:58.000Z","msg":"因為佢出軌<br />\n鐘意左第二個<br />\n先會唔解釋"},{"pid":"f6687cbc24098844857ea62046f32a3b554cc0c8","tid":1797752,"uid":145816,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"以為自己出po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff41846ee97532e9793ab89a0970bb0adb4d8bb","tid":1797752,"uid":172031,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"7b261995b00f51bb1b854317213702c79cb01065","tid":1797752,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"大家都無好好講清楚 就分開<br />\n即使我主動問 對方都唔想回應<br />\n又或者偶爾傾兩句 <br />\n但無人會想講返起件事<br />\n<br />\n明明大家一齊嗰陣 視對方咁重要<br />\n點解要告別曾經咁重要既人<br />\n但完全唔會想講清楚再走<br />\n